# 🛡️ WOP Refactoring Safety Rules

**Purpose:** Protect critical system directories from accidental modification during refactoring.

**Status:** `MANDATORY` — Violating these rules will break subsystem functionality.

---

## 🚫 Protected System Directories

These directories **MUST NOT** be modified, moved, or deleted during refactoring:

### `/.vscode`
**Reason:** VS Code workspace configuration (launch.json, tasks.json, settings.json)
**Impact:** Breaks debugging, terminal, and editor configuration
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

### `/.pi`
**Reason:** Pi runtime configuration, agent definitions, extensions, skills
**Impact:** Breaks Pi agent engine, tool execution, and extension loading
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete (only add new files)

### `/.claw`
**Reason:** Claw mode workspace and session data
**Impact:** Breaks Claw autonomous agent operations
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

### `/.wayofpi`
**Reason:** Way of Pi system files and configuration
**Impact:** Breaks Way of Pi core functionality
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

### `/agent`
**Reason:** Agent definition files and configuration
**Impact:** Breaks agent management system
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

### `/agents`
**Reason:** Agent team definitions and configurations
**Impact:** Breaks multi-agent orchestration
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

### `/agent/git/`
**Reason:** Cloned Pi extensions from upstream repo
**Impact:** Breaks Pi extension discovery and loading
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete (use `/apps/wayofpi-ui/src/extensions/` for custom extensions)

### `/.kilo`
**Reason:** Kilo editor integration files
**Impact:** Breaks Kilo editor synchronization
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

### `/.hermes`
**Reason:** Hermes client configuration and data
**Impact:** Breaks Hermes Honcho connection
**Action:** NEVER modify or delete

---

## ✅ Allowed Refactoring Areas

These directories **CAN** be modified during refactoring:

### `/apps/wayofpi-ui/src/`
**Purpose:** Way of Pi UI application source
**Allowed:** All UI components, hooks, modals, pages, utilities
**Rule:** Create new files here, never delete without verification

### `/components/` (inside apps/wayofpi-ui/src/)
**Purpose:** UI component directory
**Allowed:** Extract components here from monolithic files
**Rule:** Organize into `components/menus/`, `components/layout/`, `components/modals/`, etc.

### `/hooks/` (inside apps/wayofpi-ui/src/)
**Purpose:** Custom React hooks
**Allowed:** Extract custom hooks here
**Rule:** Verify no duplicate hooks exist before extracting

### `/pages/` (inside apps/wayofpi-ui/src/)
**Purpose:** Page components for routing
**Allowed:** Create and organize page components here
**Rule:** Ensure routing works after each change

### `/context/` (inside apps/wayofpi-ui/src/)
**Purpose:** React context providers
**Allowed:** Create and refactor context providers here
**Rule:** Test context after refactoring

### `/utils/` (inside apps/wayofpi-ui/src/)
**Purpose:** Utility functions and helpers
**Allowed:** Extract and organize utilities here
**Rule:** Ensure no circular dependencies

