## 🔍 Common Mistakes to Avoid

### ❌ Bad: Modifying protected directories
```bash
# DON'T DO THIS:
rm .vscode/launch.json
rm .pi/agents/agent.md
rm .claw/workspace/...
rm .wayofpi/config.json
rm /agent/git/*
rm .kilo/*
rm .hermes/*
```

### ✅ Good: Working in allowed directories
```bash
# DO THIS INSTEAD:
touch /apps/wayofpi-ui/src/components/NewComponent.tsx
touch /apps/wayofpi-ui/src/hooks/useNewFeature.ts
touch /apps/wayofpi-ui/src/pages/NewPage.tsx
```

### ❌ Bad: Deleting files without verification
```bash
# DON'T DO THIS:
rm /apps/wayofpi-ui/src/components/SomeComponent.tsx

# Without checking references
```

### ✅ Good: Safe deletion workflow
```bash
# DO THIS INSTEAD:
grep -r "SomeComponent" . --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx"
grep -r "SomeComponent" package.json tsconfig.json

# If no references found:
rm /apps/wayofpi-ui/src/components/SomeComponent.tsx

# Document deletion in planning document
```

